reviewText: Been wanting to see Watchmen for years and it was a pretty good movie AND AT A GREAT PRICE with three others on Bluray
Came in two days and loved the movies 8====D

I ordered this and it came on time but one of the movies was missing. Jonah Hex was not in the case. It came sealed in plastic but that movie was missing.
all four shows???? still good to watch.

4 really good comic related movies, with the possible exception of Jonah Hex.  I had not seen it before getting this collection but it was not as bad as I had heard.  I also had not seen Losers before and I really liked it.  Watchman is good but History of Violence is brillant.  And a great price.
Good collection of favorite movies for a reasonable price.
